    "%load_ext autoreload\n",
    "%autoreload 2\n",
    "%matplotlib inline\n",
    "\n",
    "import control as ctrl\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import vibrationtesting as vt\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import scipy as sp"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 54,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "M = np.diag([1,1,1])\n",
    "\n",
    "K_tuned = np.array([[3., -1, -1],[-1, 3, -1],[-1, -1, 3]])\n",
    "K = np.array([[3.03, -1, -1],[-1, 2.98, -1],[-1, -1, 3]])\n",
    "K\n",
    "\n",
    "Damping = K*.01\n",
    "Cd = np.eye(3)\n",
    "Cv = Ca = np.zeros_like(Cd)\n",
    "Bt = np.eye(3)\n",
    "\n",
    "omega, H = vt.sos_frf(M, Damping, K, Bt, Cd, Cv, Ca, .0, 3, 1, 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "vt.frfplot(omega, H)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 304,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {

    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "H_all = np.zeros((3,3000,3), dtype = 'complex128')\n",
    "for i in np.arange(1, 4):\n",
    "    for j in np.arange(1, 4):\n",
    "        omega, H_all[i-1,:,j-1] = vt.sos_frf(M, Damping/10, K, Bt, Cd, Cv, Ca, 0, 3, i, j, num_freqs = 3000)\n",
    "vt.frfplot(omega,H_all[1,:,0])    "
   ]
  },
